OL,3,CAmazon driver cried 'help' as he clung
OL,4,Cto stolen van, murder trial told
OL,6,FAn Amazon delivery driver who was
OL,7,Fkilled while trying to stop his van
OL,8,Fbeing stolen shouted "help" as he
OL,9,Fclung onto the vehicle being driven
OL,10,Faway, a court has heard.
OL,12,FClaudiu-Carol Kondor, 42, died while
OL,13,Ftrying to stop Mark Ross, 32, taking
OL,14,Fhis van while he was delivering
OL,15,Fparcels in Leeds on 20 August last
OL,16,Fyear.
