OL,3,CAmazon driver cried 'help' as he clung
OL,4,Cto stolen van, murder trial told
OL,6,FRoss has admitted manslaughter but
OL,7,Fdenies murdering Mr Kondor, from
OL,8,FSheffield, saying he was unaware he
OL,9,Fwas hanging onto the van, jurors have
OL,10,Fbeen told.
OL,12,FThe jury heard Mr Kondor was
OL,13,Fdelivering parcels for Amazon using
OL,14,Fhis own silver transit van, which was
OL,15,Ffull of packages.
OL,17,FWhile he was away from his vehicle
OL,18,Fdelivering a package, Ross allegedly
OL,19,Fclimbed into the driver's seat and
OL,20,Fstarted to drive the van away.
