OL,3,CAmazon driver cried 'help' as he clung
OL,4,Cto stolen van, murder trial told
OL,6,FRoss hit speeds of almost 60mph on
OL,7,Fresidential streets and swerved
OL,8,Ferratically from side to side before
OL,9,Fhitting two parked cars, the court
OL,10,Fheard on Thursday 6 March.
OL,12,FProsecutors say Ross "deliberately"
OL,13,Fhit the cars to "get rid of" Mr Kondor
OL,14,Fafter "speeding and swerving" failed
OL,15,Fto stop him hanging onto his van.
OL,17,FProsecutor John Harrison KC said: "The
OL,18,Fevidence suggests Mr Kondor tried to
OL,19,Fstop him by opening the front nearside
OL,20,Fpassenger door of the van and
OL,21,Fattempting to climb in."
