OL,3,CAmazon driver cried 'help' as he clung
OL,4,Cto stolen van, murder trial told
OL,6,FWitness Tracy Higson told the trial
OL,7,Fshe was driving back from a shop on
OL,8,FWingate Road in the Armley area of
OL,9,FLeeds when she was forced to skid to a
OL,10,Fstop after a van "came flying out of a
OL,11,Fside street" and nearly hit her car.
OL,13,FMs Higson said the van was "going
OL,14,Ffast" and moving "erratically", adding
OL,15,Fthat she later saw it "going from side
OL,16,Fto side".
OL,18,FShe said Mr Kondor was on the inside
OL,19,Fof the van door when she saw him and
OL,20,Fsaid he shouted "help".
