OL,3,CAmazon driver cried 'help' as he clung
OL,4,Cto stolen van, murder trial told
OL,6,F"The Amazon driver was... I just saw
OL,7,Fhim hanging off the side of the door.
OL,8,FHis hands were on the window ledge and
OL,9,Fhe was basically hanging on," she said.
OL,11,FPedestrian Lynn Spencer described how
OL,12,Fa van "whizzed past" her with a man
OL,13,F"hanging onto the side" who was "very
OL,14,Fclose to the road".
OL,16,F"I just saw the poor gentleman laid on
OL,17,Fthe floor. I saw his shoe and wallet
OL,18,Fmaybe 10 to 15 metres away from him."
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
